        "title": "Doctor: expose extra gateway service findings",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Exposes extra gateway-like services as structured doctor health findings.\n- Adds dry-run repair effects only for legacy gateway service cleanup.\n- Keeps the existing doctor:gateway-services legacy run path as the only real mutating cleanup path for normal doctor / doctor --fix.\n- Keeps gateway platform notes in the existing gateway-services core-check group, so both gateway health IDs stay ordered under the same doctor contribution.\n- Uses lazy imports from the core check so importing doctor-core-checks remains side-effect-safe in lightweight environments.\n\nThis is intentionally the small extra-service slice from the older gateway-services doctor PR. It does not migrate gateway service config repair, token drift repair, entrypoint rewrite, live-service safety, CLI --deep lint plumbing, or plugin-sensitive doctor rules.\n\n## Stack\n\nStacked on #86627. The only new gateway-services commit in this PR is 5cb287ca81; the gateway-services delta is 5 files.\n\n## Validation\n\n- `git diff --check`\n- `node node_modules/oxfmt/bin/oxfmt --check --threads=1 src/commands/doctor-gateway-services.ts src/commands/doctor-gateway-services.test.ts src/flows/doctor-core-checks.ts src/flows/doctor-health-contributions.ts src/flows/doctor-health-contributions.test.ts`\n- `node node_modules/oxlint/bin/oxlint --tsconfig config/tsconfig/oxlint.core.json src/commands/doctor-gateway-services.ts src/commands/doctor-gateway-services.test.ts src/flows/doctor-core-checks.ts src/flows/doctor-health-contributions.ts src/flows/doctor-health-contributions.test.ts`\n- `node scripts/run-tsgo.mjs -p test/tsconfig/tsconfig.core.test.json --incremental false --pretty false`\n- `node scripts/run-tsgo.mjs -p tsconfig.core.json --noEmit --incremental false --pretty false`\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/commands/doctor-gateway-services.test.ts src/flows/doctor-health-contributions.test.ts --reporter=dot --pool=forks --testTimeout=30000 --hookTimeout=30000` (2 fi